y Zancle approaching Villa San Giovanni - Punta Pezzo lighthouse in the background - 20 Oct. 2010.jpg|100px]] || 1953 || [[Punta Pezzo]]<br>{{coord|38|13|51.9|N|15|38|11.5|E}} || Fl (3) W 15s. || {{convert|26|m|ft}} || 9720 || E1770 || 15\n|- \n| [[Punta Stilo Lighthouse]] || [[File:Faro di monasterace.JPG|100px]] || 1895 || [[Monasterace]]<br>{{coord|38|26|51.2|N|16|34|39.0|E}} || Fl (3) W 15s. || {{convert|54|m|ft}} || 10584 || E2108 || 22\n|- \n| Reggio Calabria<br>Molo di Ponente Lighthouse || [http://listoflights.org/images/leuchtfeuer/gross/E1776.jpg Image] || 1883 est. || [[Reggio Calabria]]<br>{{coord|38|07|41.7|N|15|38|57.8|E}} || Iso G 2s. || {{convert|14|m|ft}} || 9736 || E1776 || 7\n|- \n| Reggio Calabria<br>Molo Sottoflutto Lighthouse || [http://listoflights.org/images/leuchtfeuer/gross/E1777.jpg Image] || 1883 est. || [[Reggio Calabria]]<br>{{coord|38|07|38.4|N|15|39|04.3|E}} || Iso R 2s. || {{convert|11|m|ft}} || 9740 || E1777 || 6\n|-\n| [[Scilla Lighthouse]] || [[File:Faro di Scilla - Castello Ruffo di Scilla - Province of Reggio Calabria, Italy - 25 Oct. 2014 - (2).jpg|100px]] || 1913 || [[Scilla, Calabria|Scilla]]<br>{{coord|38|15|22.7|N|15|42|52.4|E}} || Fl W 5s. || {{convert|72|m|ft}} || 9708 || E1766 || 22\n|- \n| Vibo Marina<br>Calata Buccarelli Lighthouse || [http://listoflights.org/images/leuchtfeuer/gross/E1757.jpg Image] || 1952 || [[Vibo Marina]]<br>{{coord|38|43|27.6|N|16|07|42.6|E}} || Fl WG 5s. || {{convert|17|m|ft}} || 9692 || E1757 || 15\n|- \n| Villa San Giovanni<br>Molo di Ponente Lighthouse || [http://listoflights.org/images/leuchtfeuer/gross/E1772.jpg Image] || 1901 est. || [[Villa San Giovanni]]<br>{{coord|38|13|07.3|N|15|37|47.7|E}} || Fl G 3s. || {{convert|14|m|ft}} || 9724 || E1772 || 7\n|- \n|}\n\n==Campania==\n\nThis is a list of lighthouses in '''[[Campania]]'''.<ref name=listoflights113/><ref name=campalazio>{{cite rowlett|itasw|accessdate= 19 November 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marina.difesa.it/cosa-facci